    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Concessimus nos <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/1927">Radelchis</persName> Dei
                        previdentia Langubardorum gentis <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs> filius
                        domni bone recordationis <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/115"
                            >Adelchis</persName>, <rs key="#Intercessory">per rogum</rs>
                        <persName key="#Intercessory #Principissa" ref="#people/3467"
                            >Arniperge</persName> dilecte coniugi nostre, tibi <persName
                            ref="#people/113" key="#Medical_doctors #Prevosts">Criscio</persName>
                        <rs key="#Prevosts">prepositus</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/85"><rs
                                key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs> Sancte Sophie</orgName> omnibus
                            <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >rebus substantiis</rs> quibus fuerunt <name ref="Walprandus"
                            >Gualprando</name> et <name ref="Maio">Maionis</name> seu <name
                            ref="Audoaldus">Audoaldo</name> germanis quibus fuerunt defensis supra
                        dicti monasterii Sancte Sophie in loco quod dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Fiscal_property #Property_of_persons_without_heirs"
                            ref="#places/3451">Collina</placeName>, veluti legibus <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Mention #Inflow #Property_of_persons_without_heirs"
                            >ad sacrum nostrum evenit palatio pro quo sine heredes decesserunt</rs>,
                        in ea videlicet ratione ut amodo et deinceps per hoc nostrum roboreum
                        preceptum supra dictis omnibus rebus uti prelegitur habere et possidere
                        valeatis tu et posteris tui et a nullis ex nostris iudicibus, id est
                        comitibus, gastaldi vel a quibuscumque agentibus habeatis aliquam
                        requisitionem, sed perpetuis temporibus possideatis. Quod vero preceptus
                        concessionis ex iussione nominate potestatis scripsi ego <persName
                            key="#Notary" ref="#people/3466">Petrus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>. Actus <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/110">Beneventus</placeName> primo anno, mense februario,
                        quarta decima indictione. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
